Package com.ebay.redlasersdk

Class Summary
BarcodeResult Results from the SDK are delivered as members of this class.
BarcodeScanActivity Base barcode activity.
BarcodeScanActivity.Status The onScanStatusUpdate() method takes a HashMap as a parameter.
BarcodeTypes This class defines the barcode types that the RedLaser SDK can recognize, and contains methods for enabling and disabling each type.
RedLaserExtras RedLaserExtras is a class containing several static methods intended to be used outside of a scan session.
 

Enum Summary
RedLaserExtras.RLScannerReadyState Result codes from the checkReadyStatus method.
